features: WATERPROOF & DURABLE ☛ The pickleball sling bag is made of tear-resistant, water-resistant, and anti-abrasion polyester fabric that can protect your pickleball gear from damage. It can be used as a typical sling bag for daily commutes, tennis sports, travel, outings, or other activities, and it is also a great gift for your pickleball fanatic.

LARGE CAPACITY & MULTI USAGE ☛ Size: 13"L*6.7" W*17.3" H. Weight: 1.3 Lb. Our sling bags feature 3 compartments and an external water bottle holder. The main compartment can hold up to 4 pickleball paddles and 12 Pickleball balls(NOTE: You can't hold so many things at the same time). The padded compartment inside the main compartment holds up to an 11-inch iPad.It can accommodate a tennis racket with a size of 102 or regular-sized, but the racket handle can only be exposed.
TONS OF POCKETS ☛ The two front pockets can hold a mobile phone, headphones, and a smaller-sized wallet. Two mesh pockets inside the middle compartment can be used for items such as power bank.

REVERSIBLE STRAPS & MULTIPURPOSE ☛ Reversible and adjustable strap means you can use it as a sling bag on either shoulder by simply unclipping the lower end of the strap and moving it to the D-ring on either side of the bag. At the same time, the single strap can be unzipped to create two individual straps, which can then be clipped on either side to create a backpack. A padded back and air-mesh shoulder strap help prevent muscle strain and shoulder pain.

HIDDEN ANTI-THEFT POCKET AND HOOK HENCE ☛ The top of the pickleball bag has a heavyweight plastic fence hook, which tucks away when not in use. This allows you to easily keep the bag safely off the ground.When carried as a backpack, the hidden pocket on the back keeps items on your back so pickpockets can't reach the contents. Great for protecting a wallet or cell phone. On the left hand side is a roomy water bottle pocket with a cord lock to keep it from falling out.

VARIOUS OCCASSINONS ☛ This tennis racket bags can be used as many outdoor activities bag, such as a pickleball paddles bag, badminton racquet bag, squash racquet bag and so on. Also it can be used as a travel backpack.Its versatile design makes it suitable for any active lifestyle.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Are the shoulder straps of this Pickleball bag adjustable? Is it suitable for people of different heights? Yes, the shoulder straps of this pickleball bag is adjustable in length, making it suitable for people of different heights. You can freely adjust the length of the shoulder straps according to your needs. What is the capacity of this Pickleball backpack? Can it accommodate my sports equipment and other gear? This pickleball bag is a large capacity bag which can easily hold two pickleball paddles and other items while zipping shut. Small tennis rackets can also be accommodated, but the handle will be exposed. Is the pickleball sling backpack suitable for all types of sports, or is it specifically designed for a certain sport? The pickleball backpack is designed to be versatile and suitable for a wide range of sports activities. Whether you play badminton, or tennis, or engage in fitness activities, this bag will accommodate your sports gear and essentials. Is there any difference between the actual color and the color shown in the website pictures? Due to different monitors and lighting conditions, there may be slight color variations between the product and color shown in website pictures. What is the material used for the pickleball backpack? Is it durable and long-lasting? The pickleball backpack is made of high-quality nylon material, which is known for its durability and longevity. It is designed to withstand the rigors of sports activities and will serve you well for a long time.
